subproject.description: UNDP in partnership with the FATA Disaster Management Authority has launched a programme entitled as “Strengthening the Foundation for Recovery, Peace and Development in FATA” in September 2011. The project aims to support the crisis affected communities in FATA to rebuild back their lives
